@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_orpkjf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.95 + ((tmp + 0.03 + v0 + 0.14) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.42)))
    v0 = tmp
    v0 = wp.abs((0.40 * (v2 + 0.25 * tmp + 0.69)))
    v2 = 0.20
    v1 = v1
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.07 - v1 + 0.95)) * (0.72 - wp.cos(v2 + 0.13)))
    data[tid] = v0
